        "Params": "{1: '1', 2: '211'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 88,
        "ActionId": 88,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": "AniZhuanchangEnd",
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'This must be stopped...'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 89,
        "ActionId": 89,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'We prepared for the worst, but the situation still deteriorated faster than everyone could anticipate...'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 90,
        "ActionId": 90,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'We tried our best to stop the Kurono researchers, but they still decided to put the Inver-Device into mass production without fully testing its reliability.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 91,
        "ActionId": 91,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'How ironic. The guns they pointed at us never worked—bullets were not any scarier than the Punishing Virus.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 92,
        "ActionId": 92,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'There were only 5 of us left in the lab long before that. Without machines, we had to stay close to the Punishing Virus.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 93,
        "ActionId": 93,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'A lot of people were infected multiple times as they were exposed to the Punishing Virus for a prolonged period. Even Dr. Kalon had his brain infected... Many more died in agony long ago due to severe decay in their bodies.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 94,
        "ActionId": 94,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'Our broken bodies were not the reason why we still did not give up. The guns pointed at us were not scarier than the Punishing Virus itself.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 95,
        "ActionId": 95,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 201,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1', 2: '500258'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 96,
        "ActionId": 96,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1', 2: 'Kurono Officer', 3: 'Sorry, but I must bring hope back to the Earth even if I have to take it with force... There\\'s no time to waste.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 97,
        "ActionId": 97,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Kurono Officer', 3: 'Hundreds or thousands may die from the Construct operation, but that\\'s still far better than the total defeat of humankind. I call it a \"necessary sacrifice.\"', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 98,
        "ActionId": 98,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 202,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1', 6: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 99,
        "ActionId": 99,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'The most disgusting guy in Kurono forced us to assist him with the mass production of the Inver-Device.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 100,
        "ActionId": 100,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'We both knew the risk involved, but this beast named \"hope\" still seized us by the throat.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 101,
        "ActionId": 101,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'After Kurono received the first batch of Inver-Device, we finally made an Inver-Device that could run stably...'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 102,
        "ActionId": 102,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'But it was all too late, whether to those who died on the operating table or to us...'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 103,
        "ActionId": 103,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'Everything we ever feared eventually happened.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 104,
        "ActionId": 104,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'The production was extremely rushed, and we inevitably had to rely on some machines. Even the most cutting-edge equipment could not detect the traces of the virus that leaked, which contaminated the machines and spread out.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 105,
        "ActionId": 105,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'The rate of the spread was limited due to the low number of machines on site, but when we realized it, some Construct models had already turned into Corrupted.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 106,
        "ActionId": 106,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": "AniZhuanchangBegin",
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'They began to hunt us down. We were only unarmed researchers with no means to protect ourselves...'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 107,
        "ActionId": 107,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 101,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory592.jpg'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 108,
        "ActionId": 108,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": "AniZhuanchangEnd",
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'Everyone else died... In the end, only Dr. Kalon and I barely made it to the place where the zero-point reactor was located. He had been unstable due to the after-effect of his brain infection.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 109,
        "ActionId": 109,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 201,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1', 2: '500270'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 110,
        "ActionId": 110,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1', 2: 'Kalon', 3: 'Look! Earth! It\\'s Earth!', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 111,
        "ActionId": 111,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'Right, one of the reasons I came here was to open the outer space shield and let the negative pressure blow all the remaining Punishing Virus into space. We could see the beautiful earth here.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 112,
        "ActionId": 112,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 302,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Stay inside the life pod, Doctor. Don\\'t leave it...', 3: '113'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 113,
        "ActionId": 113,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 202,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 114,
        "ActionId": 114,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'I stuffed Dr. Kalon and our research documents inside the only operating life pod and sent it to space. If he was lucky, perhaps a cargo ship would pick up the signal and rescue him.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 115,
        "ActionId": 115,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'But I must stay, for there was one last thing for me to do. I have to turn off the zero-point reactor array that was still running.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 116,
        "ActionId": 116,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'The system had no control program. I had to get to the core to shut it down... Just like Dr. Kalon said, I could only think of this stupidest method.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 117,
        "ActionId": 117,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'Perhaps we were too used to the convenience brought by machines. Even just walking to the core seemed to claim my remaining life—but maybe it was just my body\\'s natural reaction, given that oxygen was almost running out.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 118,
        "ActionId": 118,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'But just as I expected, the Corrupted are still functioning even after all the virus was expunged.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 119,
        "ActionId": 119,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'They have all followed me into the reactor core, trying to tear me apart at every moment.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 120,
        "ActionId": 120,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 401,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '2', 2: '1508'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 121,
        "ActionId": 121,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Corrupted', 3: 'Rargh—'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 122,
        "ActionId": 122,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'But that also gave me the perfect opportunity to lock them all here. Once I turn off the last core, this place will be completely shut and probably never open again. The reactor\\'s beautiful blue hue is no more to be seen.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 123,
        "ActionId": 123,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'There\\'s no time to write down the incident report, so I\\'m using this antique device from my personal collection... I know this recording will probably never be found.'}"
    },
    {
